I found this cover on the day after my grandad passed away. For some reason The song hit me. It was on repeat my whole 8 hour drive home from my grandads funeral. As I listened to the song I was going through some old pictures of my gramps that my grandmother gave me. Looking at my grandparents young and full of life just got me emotional. These memories are attached to this song for me since. Guys if you still have your grandparents do me a favor and show them your love and appreciation for them because you never know how much longer youâ€™ll have them with you. Thanks.
